# Coding standards
Local variables: varName
Functions: funcName
Pointers: pvarName
Smart Pointers: spvarName
Classes: ClassName
Template classes: ClassName
Tempate classes designed to be typedef'd out: T_ClassName
Class members: m_memName (also adopt pointer/smart pointer conventions)
Struct “members”: memName (again, adopt pointer/smart pointer conventions)
Macros: MACRONAME (same for parameterized/etc.)
